Description: 5Th Planet Games A/S, formerly Hugo Games A/S is a Denmark-based game development company that creates, develops and publishes online and offline mobile games globally. The Company focuses on casual mobile games, where a play session takes up to 15 minutes, and can be picked up quickly and easily. It also focuses on semi-casual games are often characterized by being multi-player games and yet multiplayer games tend to see a higher retention and monetization per active user. 5Th Planet Games A/S has a portfolio of games available on iOS and Android, including Hugo Troll Race 2, Cristiano Ronaldo: Kickâ€™nâ€™Run, Before Your Eyes, Snakebite as well as Tintin Match. The Company has two offices in Copenhagen and Berlin.
